@wp.kernel
def expr_zyurre(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v2 = wp.sin((0.69 - (tmp + 0.13 + tmp + 0.73)))
    v2 = (0.84 / v1)
    tmp = wp.exp(tmp)
    v0 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.48 * v0 + 0.44)) * ((v0 + 0.26 * v1 + 0.57) - (v2 + 0.2 * v2 + 0.86)))
    data[tid] = v0
